Package sample

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Observable
    An interface containing methods that updates information about observers.
    Observer
    An interface that allows for updating information about observers.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Controller
    Class that runs graphic interface of the application.
    Main
    Runs the application.
    Measurements
    Class storing measurements of weather condition downloaded from class WeatherStation.
    ReadFile
    Class reading temperature and pressure values from choosen file.
    SaveFile
    Class allowing to save measurements into specific file, chosen by user of application.
    Statistics
    Class allowing to calculate basic statistics of collected measurements such as mean, maximum value, minimum value and standard deviation
    WeatherStation
    Class to collecting information about weather condition in different cities around the world and storing in proper array.
